dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights on Nile Delta map. Cairo map: "Cartography by Andrew Alfred-Duggan." Nile Delta map: "Cartography by Nguyen Hanh." Includes index of streets, location map, Cairo Metro guide, photographs, and color illustrations.
